node.text: ðŸ™‚ 12:01 am....It is a new day. What an amazing journey of a year this has been for me. I want to thank an amazing and awesome God of mine for allowing me to journey through it safely from birthday to birthday. I never would have thought I would make it this far to the big number 44 as at times even I wondered if I was going to make it. An amazing journey for me as I journeyed my journey and made my rounds. From Los Angeles, CA skid row to Las Vegas, Nv., Hong Kong, Dallas, Tx., Orlando, Fl., and even Davao City, Philippines. I am greatful for all the experiences both in the good times and the rough times as well this year life still is my classroom. It was an honor and a privilege to experience one of my best friends and brother win Thrilla in Davao boxing event this past June. Being able to travel internationally and be in his corner for the fight I'm proud of that and never will forget it. Speaking to media at a media event outside the USA as well the rush of promoting the hype at the weigh-in all priceless memories I can't even truly explain it all. Thank you to everyone along my journey this year. All the amazing and special people like you for making it so tremendous and wonderful. From coast to coast and worldwide if you like me or if you don't like me smile as today is my birthday. I'm smiling! If you get a chance do me a favor today, go help somebody today for no reason. Be kind to one another out there today. My heart and my thoughts are with you all today! ðŸ™‚
